OL,5, The Vatican has reiterated its staunch 
OL,6, opposition to sex changes, gender      
OL,7, theory, surrogate parenthood, abortion 
OL,8, and euthanasia in a text dubbed        
OL,9, "Dignitas Infinita" (Infinite Dignity).
OL,11,FOther social themes, such as poverty,  
OL,12,Fmigration and human trafficking are    
OL,13,Falso emphasised as being potential     
OL,14,Fthreats to human dignity.              
OL,16,FThe text was signed by Pope Francis.   
OL,18,FThe pontiff has often been criticised  
OL,19,Fby Catholic conservatives over his     
OL,20,Fperceived liberal stance.              
